NG0234:2: shri a yuhpa ti ra ka la tan+t+ra /
NG0234:3: e man+ta twa ta dzi bin ra ga ka so ri na ma /
NG0234:5: dpal tshe bdag nag po'i rgyud /
NG0234:6: drag sngags kyi de kho na srog dmar len gyi spu gri zhes bya ba /
NG0234:7: dpal tshe bdag nag po bde ba chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0234:8: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa'i dus gcig na /
NG0234:9: bcom ldan 'das chos nyid kyi pho brang na /
NG0234:10: khyab gdal chen po'i gnas zhe sdang chen po rnam par dag pa'i gzhal yas na /
NG0234:12: rdo rje yongs su 'dzin pa dang */
NG0234:13: bde ba'i ye shes can dang */
NG0234:14: bgrod pa phyin ci ma log pa dang */
NG0234:16: gar dgu'i chos kyi phyag rgya 'bar ba'i rnam pa dang */
NG0234:17: lam las gol ba'i rdzu 'phrul can rnams dang thabs
NG0234:18: cig tu zhe sdang chen po 'dul ba'i ting nge
NG0234:20: de nas 'jig rten gsum gyi phyogs bcu g.yos par gyur te /
NG0234:21: 'khor rnams rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshogs /
NG0234:22: 'jigs shing skrag nas brgyal la khad do //
NG0234:23: 'khor de'i nang nas rig pa'i stobs can longs te gsol pa //
NG0234:24: bcom ldan 'das 'dus pa'i tshogs rnams 'khor du mchi /
NG0234:25: 'khor la thugs rje ma chung mdzod //
NG0234:26: mgo lus snying yang 'gas pa snyam //
NG0234:27: gdung ba'i shugs kyis nye bar mdzod //
NG0234:29: de nas bcom ldan 'das ting nge 'dzin de las bzhengs te dgyes pa'i nga ro 'di ston @#//
NG0234:31: sngags sor bzhag / a e ha ha ya ga
NG0234:32: sha de pa ti su ma ra ram ram zhes
NG0234:33: bsgrags so // 'khor thams cad rang rang gi yid
NG0234:34: rang bzhin gyi me ru 'bar nas tshig cing brlag
NG0234:35: bsgrags so // la khad do // de nas bcom
NG0234:36: ldan 'das kyis 'khor de dag gi rang rang gi
NG0234:38: bcom ldan 'das dpal khrag 'thung gi rgyal po tshe bdag nag pos /
NG0234:39: nyid kyi srog gi snying po de kho na nyid yang nas yang du rnam par bsgrags so //
NG0234:40: e e e e zhes brjod pas chos thams cad rang bzhin med pa ma skyes pa //
NG0234:42: nam mkha' lta bur rang grol pa'o //
NG0234:43: de la chos thams cad 'byung zhing ye shes rang la gnas so //
NG0234:44: de la chos thams cad drag po'i gtum rngam 'bar
NG0234:45: bas ye shes thig le'i ngang du rang bcom mo
NG0234:46: // de la chos thams cad zhe sdang 'bar ba'i
NG0234:47: me yis rtog 'dzin thams cad bsregs te rang skam
NG0234:48: nas ye shes rang gsal lo //
NG0234:49: de las 'khor thams cad ye shes skyes te rang
NG0234:50: rang gi srog gi snying po thams cad mdongs gsol
NG0234:51: du phul lo // de la thugs kyi sprul pa tshe bdag nag po mgo dgu pa yis /
NG0234:52: ka zhes zhes rngam par bsgrags pas phrin las thams
NG0234:53: cad lhun gyis grub cing yongs su rdzogs par gyur
NG0234:54: to / de nas yum gsod byed kyi rgyal mos myags shes phul bas /
NG0234:55: log pa'i srog dbang du 'dus nas ye shes kyi thig ler gsal ba'o //
NG0234:56: phyag na rdo rjes rngubs shes phul bas ye shes
NG0234:57: chen po'i mes khrag dang bag chags bskams nas phyag
NG0234:58: rgya brtan par rang gsal ba'o //
NG0234:59: rus sbal gyi rgyal pos mugs shes bsgrags pas /
NG0234:60: 'gro ba rmongs pa'i srog bsdus te /
NG0234:61: bla dang tshe srog bcangs te chos nyid du rang grol ba'o //
NG0234:62: ya ma ra tsa sa ya zhes pas /
NG0234:63: rang gi las kyi rlung gis lha dang lus srog phrogs nas /
NG0234:64: ye shes bla ma'i sar bgrod pa'o //
NG0234:65: bya khyung gi rgyal pos shag ces pas /
NG0234:66: gdug pa'i dug rlangs thams cad bcom nas /
NG0234:67: nye bar bgrod pa thob pa'o //
NG0234:68: las kyi tshe bdag nag pos dun zhes phul bas /
NG0234:69: srid pa'i srog rten zhi nas 'od dmar nag 'thibs pa phrogs nas /
NG0234:70: kun tu bzang po bde ba chen por rang grol ba'o //
NG0234:71: de nas mon pa seng ge'i mgo can gyis /
NG0234:72: srog la bam ram kha thum yam yam rbad /
NG0234:74: srog gi rten gzhi gcod par 'gyur ro //
NG0234:75: de nas mon pa stag gi mgo can gyis /
NG0234:76: srog la hril myags thum shag rbad /
NG0234:78: dwangs ma bzhi yis rang rang gcod par gyur to //
NG0234:79: mon pa dred kyi mgo can gyis /
NG0234:80: srog la gzir thums ram thun rbad /
NG0234:82: srog gi dwangs snyigs phyed pa gyur to /
NG0234:83: mon pa khyung gi mgo can gyis /
NG0234:84: srog la ma ra ya thun rbad /
NG0234:86: srog gi bla mtsho bskams par gyur to //
NG0234:87: bdud kyi srog gshed chen po bzhis /
NG0234:91: la thun rmugs tsit+ta breng shag dza /
NG0234:93: srog la thun gzer shag rbad /
NG0234:96: tshogs drug rten las 'phos par gyur to //
NG0234:97: de nas srid pa'i lha gdon drag po rnams kyis /
NG0234:98: srog la ma ra ya rbad /
NG0234:106: bsod nams che ba'i lus srog dang bral bar gyur to //
NG0234:107: de nas btsan gyi rgyal po rnams kyis /
NG0234:111: lus kyi 'byung ba dkrugs te 'pho bar gyur to //
NG0234:112: de nas rgyal po sde bzhis srog la breng breng rbad /
NG0234:119: rgyu bdun gegs su skyes par gyur to //
NG0234:120: de nas bdud kyi rkya dmag 'bum sdes /
NG0234:121: srog rtsa khrag ting snying phyung thums ril ram shag rbad /
NG0234:123: zhes phul bas nang khrol smad lnga gtubs par gyur to //
NG0234:124: de nas srin po pho mos /
NG0234:125: e bam ram khram shig tsit+ta rngubs /
NG0234:126: dgra bo'i srog la thun rmugs ling shag rbad /
NG0234:129: de nas ma mo'i tshogs 'bum sdes /
NG0234:134: rnam shes rten las 'pho bar gyur to //
NG0234:136: srog la bam ril ram shag rbad /
NG0234:137: tsit+ta byer thum hur thums dza /
NG0234:138: zhes phul bas rims dal yams kyi nad 'bebs par gyur to //
NG0234:139: de nas gdug pa gsum gyi tshogs kyis /
NG0234:140: srog la bam ril ram shag rbad /
NG0234:143: gdug pa'i spu gris lus srog gcod par gyur to //
NG0234:144: de nas sde brgyad gza' dang lha srin gyis /
NG0234:148: rbud yam thun yam hril shag b+h+yo //
NG0234:149: zhes phul bas srog dbugs dang lo tog rtsi bcud thams cad bcad de 'pho ba'o //
NG0234:150: de nas stobs can rnams kyi mthu dril te /
NG0234:151: srog la rbad thum ril rbad /
NG0234:155: rtsa dang srog zungs bcad de 'pho ba'o //
NG0234:156: dregs pa can thams cad kyi mthu stobs dril te /
NG0234:157: snying gzer sbur nan ha la ha la tsa ma ri phyung */
NG0234:161: rang gi mthus gzir ba dang */
NG0234:165: de nas 'khor de dag rab tu 'dus nas /
NG0234:166: dgyes pa'i mdangs rnyed par 'gyur ro //
NG0234:167: de nas bcom ldan 'das khrag 'thung gi rgyal po des /
NG0234:168: e he he he e hur thums dza /
NG0234:170: nye bar las la brtson pa'i tshul gyis rang rang gi shes pa'i rgyud la 'dus te thim @#//
NG0234:172: bdud dang gshed rang gi rgyud las ldang zhing */
NG0234:173: rang gcod kyi mtshon cha bskul bas /
NG0234:174: rtsa dang srog zungs rang gshed gcod cing */
NG0234:175: khrag dang bag chags rang skyes te /
NG0234:176: thod par snying po dang srog sdud pa'o //
NG0234:177: dpal tshe bdag nag po srog dmar len gyi rgyud las /
NG0234:178: gleng gzhi rtsa ba'i le'u ste dang po'o // //
NG0234:179: de nas 'khor rdo rje snying pos bcom ldan 'das
NG0234:180: la gsol pa / rgyal ba kun gyi rang bzhin dngos //
NG0234:181: gsang sngags ngo bo de nyid lags //
NG0234:183: dregs pa'i mthu rtsal ldan pa kun //
NG0234:184: srog snying dbul zhing las la gnyer //
NG0234:185: bka' bzhin nye ba ji lta bu //
NG0234:186: lhun grub zil gnon phyag rgya bstan //
NG0234:187: gnyen po gang phyir brjid pa'i sku //
NG0234:188: drag pos gdul bya gang lags pa //
NG0234:189: 'khor la rgyas par bshad du gsol //
NG0234:191: bcom ldan 'das kyis dri ba gsum gyi don rgyas par bshad do //
NG0234:192: bskal pa rdzogs ldan bya ba la //
NG0234:193: rigs las gol ba'i khro bo la //
NG0234:194: nag po 'thom byed bdud kyi gtso //
NG0234:195: srid pa'i mnga' bdag khrag skyugs gcod //
NG0234:196: rtsub khro srog gcod ging gi gtso //
NG0234:197: zhe sdang gdug pa gdug khro'i gtso //
NG0234:198: phung byed nag po tshe yi bdag / 'byung ba bzhi yi rngam 'og na //
NG0234:199: brgyad gnyis drug gnyis bzhi dbus na //
NG0234:200: lus chen yan lag rags la rngam //
NG0234:201: skra dang kha spu ag tshom rtsub //
NG0234:202: stod smad srin pa'i rlon gyi shun //
NG0234:203: mgo dang snying gi phreng bas brgyan //
NG0234:204: mtshon cha me rlung dug gi mtshon //
NG0234:206: myur du gsod cing sha rlon za //
NG0234:207: mngal du 'tshub cing rak+ta 'dzag / thod rus 'bru mar dkrugs shing 'thungs /
NG0234:208: ded dpon bzhi yi 'khor la rbod //
NG0234:209: chags pa'i rgya mtsho myos par byed //
NG0234:210: gdug pa'i me yis rang rgyud bsreg / de lta bu yi sde bzhi'i gtso //
NG0234:211: ru tra nag po tshe yi bdag / de yi bstan pa gting nas dkrugs //
NG0234:213: 'gro ba ma lus bsdus shing gsod //
NG0234:214: de yang ji lta bu zhe na //
NG0234:215: bde ba'i dbang phyug ded dpon zhes //
NG0234:216: rigs kyi bdag por grags pa cig / gsang sngags de nyid ris su phye //
NG0234:217: brda' don ma grol lhug par spyad //
NG0234:218: bgrod pa ma thob dpe las mtshon //
NG0234:219: rang nyams ma rnyed brkam chags spyad //
NG0234:220: rigs ngan mo la grogs su spyod //
NG0234:221: sha chen keng rus rgyan la rol //
NG0234:222: gsang sngags bka' bsgo log pa yis //
NG0234:223: dus ma yin par tshe 'phos nas //
NG0234:224: na rag rdo rje dmyal bar ltung *//
NG0234:225: bzhi brgya mtha' ru sdug bsngal myong *//
NG0234:226: chad las rgal te bde bas brel //
NG0234:227: bskal pa bzhi nas brgyad gnyis 'khor //
NG0234:228: tsha grang gnas nas bskal pa bzhir //
NG0234:229: 'khor zhing sdug bsngal zad mtha' ru //
NG0234:231: bskal pa gnyis su sdug cing 'khyams //
NG0234:232: de mthar phyi nang sgrib pa'i gnas //
NG0234:235: rnag khrag ngan skyugs lcags thum mid //
NG0234:236: bskal pa gcig tu sdug cing 'khyams //
NG0234:237: de mthar rdzu 'phrul drag po'i gnas //
NG0234:238: lcags mkhar bcu gnyis brgyad gnyis 'obs //
NG0234:239: thod mkhar bzhi dbus sha khrag za //
NG0234:240: rngam pa'i nga ros 'khor rnams mngags //
NG0234:241: de ltar rnam smin mang bsags pas //
NG0234:242: gnas su ru tra nag por smin //
NG0234:243: de yis 'jig rten phung byed na //
NG0234:244: rgyal ba kun gyi thugs rgyud nas //
NG0234:245: byin rlabs mthu rtsal stobs 'gran te //
NG0234:246: nag po de nyid 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0234:247: sangs rgyas cho 'phrul sna tshogs mdzad //
NG0234:248: stong pa'i rang bzhin de stong kyang *//
NG0234:249: stong pas nag po sde ma stongs //
NG0234:250: sangs rgyas rdul snyed zhing khams 'dod //
NG0234:251: nag po'i sha khrag rngam zhing rol //
NG0234:252: des ma bskyod phyir stobs chen gsum //
NG0234:253: ya ma badzra ha la'i sku //
NG0234:254: rang rang lag cha cha byad 'khor //
NG0234:255: sngags tshig drag po rngam bzlas nas //
NG0234:256: nag po tshe yi bdag po la //
NG0234:257: lus ngag skong phyir me rlung sbrul //
NG0234:258: nad dang mtshon cha'i char phab nas //
NG0234:259: nag po 'khor bcas dga' mgu nas //
NG0234:260: sha khrag ro dang bdud rtsir 'gyur //
NG0234:261: mnga' brnyes sde las rgyal la khad //
NG0234:262: des ma thul nas khro bor bya /
NG0234:263: khro bo sme ba brtsegs pa yis //
NG0234:264: rdo rje srin po 'khor dang bcas //
NG0234:265: nag po bsgral la bza' bar rngams //
NG0234:266: gsang sngags gdug pa'i nga ror bton //
NG0234:267: ye shes me yis sras mchog sprul //
NG0234:268: tshe bdag drag po gshin rje yis //
NG0234:269: ki la tsit+ta'i dkyil du bza' //
NG0234:270: btab pas sme brtsegs de nyid rgyal //
NG0234:271: rdo rje srin po'i 'khor brlags nas //
NG0234:272: nag po dregs pa'i tshe bkrag phrogs //
NG0234:273: sangs rgyas rdzu 'phrul zhi bar byas //
NG0234:274: des ma thul te dgongs pa bsdus //
NG0234:275: gsang sngags ngo bo de kho na //
NG0234:276: dwangs ma chen po lnga yi dngos //
NG0234:277: ye shes lnga nyid de rtogs pa'i //
NG0234:278: rigs lnga'i gtso bo spyi yi gzugs //
NG0234:279: ka la mthing nag brjid pa'i sku //
NG0234:280: zil gnon phyag rgya chen po nyid //
NG0234:281: stong nyid ma skyes 'gag med pa'i //
NG0234:282: lhun grub ye shes thams cad mkhyen //
NG0234:283: lhun po ri rab brtan ltar brjid //
NG0234:284: rnam par dbu gsum sku gsung thugs //
NG0234:285: rgyud drug 'khor ba bsgral ba'i rtags //
NG0234:286: pha rol phyin phyag ye shes drug / skye ba rnam bzhi dag pa'i rtags //
NG0234:287: tshad med zhabs bzhi rdzu 'phrul rkang *//
NG0234:288: sra byed brtan pas thams cad gnon //
NG0234:289: mnyen byed bskyil zhing sdud pa'i dbang *//
NG0234:290: gsal byed khrag chu bag chags bsregs //
NG0234:291: g.yeng byed rkyen med rang shugs ldan //
NG0234:293: rgyu rkyen thabs la rag ma lus //
NG0234:294: bde ba chos sku stong bdag med //
NG0234:295: stong las kun skyes bsam dpag dka' //
NG0234:296: nag po 'dul phyir sna tshogs sprul //
NG0234:297: ya ma badzra khyams khang khyung *//
NG0234:298: de bzhin gnyis ldan seng ge stag / gdug pa'i ye shes khro chung 'bar //
NG0234:299: tshul dgu chas dgu rgyan dgu @#//
NG0234:301: gar dgu stabs dgu rngam sgra dgu //
NG0234:302: thod sbrul rin po che la sogs //
NG0234:303: gsod byed khrag skyug tshogs kun gnon //
NG0234:305: be con gtun shing sdigs 'dzub brdeg / nag po gel pa bsgyel te mnan //
NG0234:307: yang sprul drug khri drug stong bcas //
NG0234:308: rngam zhing dregs pa'i 'gying stabs kyis //
NG0234:309: nag po 'khor bcas gdan du bting *//
NG0234:310: nag po brgyal sangs 'dar zhing sleb //
NG0234:311: zil gnon phyag rgya'i gdan du gsol //
NG0234:312: 'khor rnams dbang bsdus mdangs dang phral //
NG0234:313: 'khor du las kyi sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0234:314: snam nas slar bton bran khol bskos //
NG0234:315: srog gi snying po rang dbang bsdus //
NG0234:316: nag pos rngam pa'i sme jags bton //
NG0234:317: bdag cag rgyal ba'i 'khor lags kyis //
NG0234:318: 'khor la thugs rje ma chung mdzod //
NG0234:319: bka' la thogs shig bka' bzhin 'gyid //
NG0234:320: ci bcol las rnams bka' bzhin nyan //
NG0234:322: de phyir rgyud 'di drag jags bshad //
NG0234:323: ces 'khor la rgyas par gsungs so //
NG0234:324: drags sngags kyi de kho na nyid srog dmar len
NG0234:325: spu gri las dregs pa can btul ba'i le'u ste
NG0234:326: gnyis pa'o /// de nas 'khor gyi nang nas rdo rje 'dzin pa stan las langs nas /
NG0234:328: kye ho bcom ldan khrag 'thung dpal //
NG0234:329: las rnams kun gyi rtsa ba ru //
NG0234:330: brnag pa'i rgyal po dmar len la //
NG0234:331: rtsa ba dag dang man ngag gi / las kyi rnam grangs bshad du gsol //
NG0234:333: bcom ldan 'das kyis snying po don gyi man ngag rgyas pa bshad do //
NG0234:334: dmar len don gyi man ngag las //
NG0234:335: rtsa ba rnam pa gnyis su bshad //
NG0234:336: thun mong dang ni khyad par ro //
NG0234:337: thun mong sbyor ba rnam pa lnga //
NG0234:338: 'bru bzhi'i sbyor ba drug gnyis bzhi //
NG0234:339: kun 'byung rtsa ba brgyad gnyis gcig / gab pa'i sbyor ba bzhi gnyis ldan //
NG0234:340: gsad gzir gnan gzir bsrung dang dbab //
NG0234:341: bsreg dang srog dbrog dbral bar shis //
NG0234:342: yan lag sdig pa'i phag mo gnyis //
NG0234:343: skye ba rlung bshig rang bdud 'phel //
NG0234:344: rnal mar spog dang tsher spogs dkrug / 'pho tshul
NG0234:345: gnyis ldan bde ba gcig / ye shes rig pa
NG0234:346: rang rtsal bgrod // kun gyi mtha' ru 'byung ba dkrug / thun mong phung byed sdig pa 'joms //
NG0234:347: 'byung ba gnam bstan gnyis ldan pa //
NG0234:348: ma sbyangs dag pa'i tshul du bgrod /
NG0234:349: khyad par las rim gsum gnyis gcig / phye ba'i rim pa bde dang ldan /
NG0234:350: khyab gsal spogs med bde dang ldan //
NG0234:351: snying po mchog gi rtsa bar gsungs //
NG0234:352: gnyen pos 'phen cing gcod par bskul //
NG0234:353: spu gri'i las su gcod cing sdud //
NG0234:354: rang grub bdud gshed 'chi bdag ldang *//
NG0234:355: rang gsal bskul bas ya yis bskyod //
NG0234:356: thugs rje shugs sgrol thar pa'i lam //
NG0234:357: bde ba'i ye shes rang nyid @#//
NG0234:359: phyag rgya rang gsal bgrod thob med //
NG0234:360: 'gag med snying po mchog nyid gsal //
NG0234:361: bden pa gnyis med chos skur gcig / thams cad 'joms sgrol bde chen nyid //
NG0234:362: nyid las gzhan du btsal yang med //
NG0234:363: gser bug snying po rang bstan yin //
NG0234:364: kun thub snying po las dbang 'joms //
NG0234:365: srog ces bya ba 'pho bar byed //
NG0234:366: gnyis med rig pa lha ru gsal //
NG0234:367: srin mo las kyi mtha' ru 'pho //
NG0234:368: sbyor ba lhan cig lnga'am gsum //
NG0234:369: rgyal ba'i bka' thub rgyal mtheb mngag / rang nyid che ba'i gnas la gnas //
NG0234:370: lo thog gzhom pa'i las gsum gyis //
NG0234:372: bsrung ba'i rgyal po gcig tu dril //
NG0234:373: nye ba'i dbang po rang gnas gzir //
NG0234:374: dug dang sbyor ba byad gzhug 'byin //
NG0234:375: las dang sbyor ba gshog cing gcod //
NG0234:376: tsit+ta'i dkyil nas rnam shes 'phrog / lus med dbang po yid kyis 'joms //
NG0234:377: de med sbyor ba yug pa brkyang *//
NG0234:378: rang gshed rang bdud rang la ldang *//
NG0234:379: rang rgyud rang gnas gsum gnyis gcig / gnas dang slong dang rkyen dang gcod //
NG0234:380: 'pho dang bgrod dang srog sdud bcas //
NG0234:381: las de chos nyid rang grol yin //
NG0234:382: mtha' ru lhun grub bsreg dang sbyar //
NG0234:383: nam mkha' bar snang sa gzhi la //
NG0234:384: bsreg mnan gcod pa'i 'khor lo bca' //
NG0234:385: mngag dang gzir dang bstab dang dbul //
NG0234:386: las gnyer gtad mthar zor dang mnan //
NG0234:387: rang gi ye shes gsal zhing 'bar //
NG0234:388: me dang tsha ba bsreg cing bdo //
NG0234:389: sbyor ba mngon du gsad dang 'pho //
NG0234:390: dkar nag las de gab sbas gsang *//
NG0234:391: las tshogs rgyas pa lhun gyis grub //
NG0234:392: rgyud kyi rang bzhin bdun nam gcig / sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi rgyud //
NG0234:393: blta spyod 'khor lo dam tshig dbang *//
NG0234:394: las rim sbyor ba 'brel bcas yin //
NG0234:395: gzhi lam 'bras bu lhun grub gcig / phyi nang gsang ba bshad pa'i mtha' //
NG0234:396: kun 'dus rig pa'i mtshon char bshad //
NG0234:397: srog dmar len spu gri'i rgyud las /
NG0234:398: dngos gzhi bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o // //
